greeting_message: Good Morning, {{name}}. Welcome to your My Service Account
link_notification_center: Go to Notifications and Message Center
text_info_one: If you did not receive email alerts when the new important EI information is available in your Service Canada Digital Centre account, you can go to my preferences and update those settings
text_info_two: If you recently applied for a benefit online the approval process maytake up to five business days
text_info_three: If you need help, you can press the “Need Help” button and our virtual concierge can assist
text_info_four: Information on Employment Insurance (EI), pensions, benefits and taxes, for those who work or live outside of Canada
